    <note>Guo(1) Maoxun [953] His ancestors were Taiyuan jun Guo(1). Yuanming's son [3458], Quan's [942] grandson, Zhang(1) Feng's [7011] son-in-law. His maternal great grandfather was Li(2) Yingji [1120]. His sister was Su(1) Song's [8116] daughter-in-law. His son, Taichong [24823], was related by marriage to Lu(3) Yundi [8097] and I am guessing that Yundi was Maoxun's son-in-law. XCB, 298.17b, 314.1b-2a, 314.11b, 315.2b, 335.20b, 340.9b, 347.16a, 372.14a, 395.13b, 13b (n.), 403.2b, 432.2b, 454.6a, 483.1a (n.), 485.9b, 499.14a, 501.1a; XCBSB, 10.15b; SHY:ZG, 43.53b-56b, 56b-58a, 59a-61a, 62b-63a, 63b; SHY:SH, 49.24a, Su Song, WJ, 59.9b. CBD, 3, 2143-4.</note>
